{"tid":1635181,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[講定先] 林鄭只剩返最後一招，如果我地頂到就嬴硬","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:08.000Z","uid":108757,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ce8a13929be9a6c78ead5fd8b3098b0ecbc45c0","tid":1635181,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭只剩返最後一招︰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用黑警卧底進行恐怖襲擊殺死市民，嫁禍抗爭者。</span><br />\n例如︰燒鋪燒埋樓上住宅、卧底放炸彈、炸巴士、炸地鐵......<br />\n結果︰示威變恐怖襲擊，市民割席，國際割席<br />\n唔好話林鄭做唔出，佢一定做得出，宜家狗已經係恐怖份子。<br />\n<br />\n應對方法︰<br />\n1. 君子有所為，有所不為。手足必須保持<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理性、獨立思考</span>，絕對唔可以變成恐怖份子。<br />\n恐怖主義定義參考︰<br />\nTerrorism is defined in the Oxford Dictionary as &ldquo;the unlawful use of violence and intimidation, <span style=\"color: red;\">especially against civilians</span>, in the pursuit of political aims.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://ourworldindata.org/terrorism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fourworldindata.org%2Fterrorism&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=06042fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://ourworldindata.org/terrorism</a><br />\n<br />\nTerrorism is, in the broadest sense, the use of intentional violence, generally <span style=\"color: red;\">against civilians</span>, for political purposes.<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrorism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTerrorism&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=9e2e29bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terrorism</a><br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對所有恐怖主義行為、恐怖襲擊，必須第一時間果斷割席</span>，因為到時實有風向撚出嚟叫大家唔好割席。詳情請參考以下PO。<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 對一切唔屬於恐怖主義行為，手足只做一樣野，就係向外界(國際、本地)<span style=\"color: red;\">解釋背後原因</span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對不割席</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\nFight For Freedom, Stand With HK</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">MON PO 狗唔洗痴心妄想，你地無得嬴，快啲辭職移民啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4d4b73d72ac057f3630a2a5cfdec3ce77c266f65","tid":1635181,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:06.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"815d2815f9ed88f9a6f0f4d108c2db529263ea37","tid":1635181,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80ce61a9baa4c3db81d322a8dcb31cf83a56013","tid":1635181,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"新口號：和勇相連 永不割蓆！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nctCghi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnctCghi.jpg&h=d2039aa1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48231bf71a787b49be6059e40d89f59a3d7f2d25","tid":1635181,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce8a13929be9a6c78ead5fd8b3098b0ecbc45c0","tid":1635181,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭只剩返最後一招︰<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用黑警卧底進行恐怖襲擊殺死市民，嫁禍抗爭者。</span><br />\n例如︰燒鋪燒埋樓上住宅、卧底放炸彈、炸巴士、炸地鐵......<br />\n結果︰示威